content.rendered:
Directed by Soori. Abhi.

Written by Kiran Kaverappa. Soori. Maasthi Upparahalli.

Cast Shivarajkumar(Shiva). Manvita Kamath(Punarvasu (as Manvitha Harish)). Dhananjaya(Dolly). Bhavana(Panchami). Devaraj(Ramachandra) .M.N. Lakshmi Devi.Achyuth Kumar. Poornachandra Mysuru(Jamoon Ravi (as Poornachandra Mysore)). Triveni Rao(Constable Saroja). Vasishta N. Simha(Chitte). Rockline Sudhakar(Subbi). Cockroach Sudhi(Cockroach (as Sudhir))

Languages Kannada.

Producers K.P. Srikanth.

Production Venus Entertainers.
